---
// Testimonials & Pricing Preview Section
---

<section class="w-full max-w-7xl z-20 mt-0 mr-auto mb-32 ml-auto pt-6 pr-6 pb-6 pl-6 relative">
    <div class="flex flex-col text-center mb-20 items-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-orange-500/20 bg-orange-500/5 mb-6">
            <span class="text-xs font-semibold text-orange-200 uppercase tracking-widest font-sans">Testimonials</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="md:text-7xl text-5xl font-medium text-white tracking-tighter font-manrope mb-6">Proven results, <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-zinc-200 to-zinc-500">delivered</span></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24">
         <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 relative">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic mb-6">"MoonTax fixed two years of missing DeFi transactions across five chains. Their CPA caught errors my previous accountant never saw. Worth every penny."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
                <div>
                    <h5 class="text-white font-semibold">D. Roberts</h5>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Crypto Founder</span>
                </div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="bg-zinc-900/40 p-8 rounded-[2rem] border border-white/5 relative">
            <p class="text-lg text-gray-300 leading-relaxed italic mb-6">"I was randomly selected for a crypto audit. MoonTax handled everything and got it cleared with zero penalties."</p>
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4">
                <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-zinc-700"></div>
                <div>
                    <h5 class="text-white font-semibold">S. Jensen</h5>
                    <span class="text-xs text-gray-500">Investor</span>
                </div>
            </div>
         </div>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mb-8">
        <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium text-white mb-2">Clear Pricing With No Surprises</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-400">Every client has different data volume and complexity. We provide fast, transparent quotes.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 text-sm text-gray-300">
        <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full border border-white/10">Starter</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full border border-white/10">Advanced</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full border border-white/10">Pro</span>
        <span class="px-4 py-2 bg-white/5 rounded-full border border-white/10">Enterprise</span>
    </div>
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
        <button class="text-orange-400 hover:text-white border-b border-orange-400 hover:border-white transition-colors pb-0.5">Get Your Free Quote</button>
    </div>
</section>

